{"title": "File Upload & Download", "source": "netexec", "source_label": "NetExec Wiki", "path": "ftp-protocol/get-and-put-files", "html": "<h1 id=\"file-upload-download\">File Upload &amp; Download</h1>\n<h2 id=\"download-a-file\">Download a File</h2>\n<p>Download a file from the FTP server.</p>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>nxc<span class=\"w\"> </span>ftp<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;username&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;password&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>--get<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;filename&gt;\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>Expected Results:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-bash\">nxc ftp &lt;TARGET&gt; -u &lt;USERNAME&gt; -p D2xc9CgD --get ftp_flag.thm</code></pre>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>nxc<span class=\"w\"> </span>ftp<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;TARGET&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;USERNAME&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span>D2xc9CgD<span class=\"w\"> </span>--get<span class=\"w\"> </span>ftp_flag.thm\nFTP<span class=\"w\">         </span><span class=\"m\">10</span>.10.176.246<span class=\"w\">   </span><span class=\"m\">21</span><span class=\"w\">     </span><span class=\"m\">10</span>.10.176.246<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"o\">[</span>*<span class=\"o\">]</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>Banner:<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span>vsFTPd<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">3</span>.0.3<span class=\"o\">)</span>\nFTP<span class=\"w\">         </span><span class=\"m\">10</span>.10.176.246<span class=\"w\">   </span><span class=\"m\">21</span><span class=\"w\">     </span><span class=\"m\">10</span>.10.176.246<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"o\">[</span>+<span class=\"o\">]</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>frank:D2xc9CgD\nFTP<span class=\"w\">         </span><span class=\"m\">10</span>.10.176.246<span class=\"w\">   </span><span class=\"m\">21</span><span class=\"w\">     </span><span class=\"m\">10</span>.10.176.246<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"o\">[</span>+<span class=\"o\">]</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>Downloaded:<span class=\"w\"> </span>ftp_flag.thm\n</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"upload-a-file\">Upload a File</h2>\n<p>Upload a file to the FTP server providing you have relevant permissions. The first argument after <code>--put</code> will be the location of the file on your local machine to upload. The second argument determines the path and filename:</p>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>nxc<span class=\"w\"> </span>ftp<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;username&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;password&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>--put<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;local-file&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;remote-path&gt;\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>Expected Results:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-bash\">nxc ftp &lt;TARGET&gt; -u &lt;USERNAME&gt; -p D2xc9CgD --put test.txt test.txt</code></pre>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>nxc<span class=\"w\"> </span>ftp<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;TARGET&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;USERNAME&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span>D2xc9CgD<span class=\"w\"> </span>--put<span class=\"w\"> </span>test.txt<span class=\"w\"> </span>test.txt\nFTP<span class=\"w\">         </span><span class=\"m\">10</span>.10.176.246<span class=\"w\">   </span><span class=\"m\">21</span><span class=\"w\">     </span><span class=\"m\">10</span>.10.176.246<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"o\">[</span>*<span class=\"o\">]</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>Banner:<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span>vsFTPd<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">3</span>.0.3<span class=\"o\">)</span>\nFTP<span class=\"w\">         </span><span class=\"m\">10</span>.10.176.246<span class=\"w\">   </span><span class=\"m\">21</span><span class=\"w\">     </span><span class=\"m\">10</span>.10.176.246<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"o\">[</span>+<span class=\"o\">]</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>frank:D2xc9CgD\nFTP<span class=\"w\">         </span><span class=\"m\">10</span>.10.176.246<span class=\"w\">   </span><span class=\"m\">21</span><span class=\"w\">     </span><span class=\"m\">10</span>.10.176.246<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"o\">[</span>+<span class=\"o\">]</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>Uploaded:<span class=\"w\"> </span>test.txt<span class=\"w\"> </span>to<span class=\"w\"> </span>test.txt\n</code></pre></div>", "excerpt": "File Upload &amp; Download Download a File Download a file from the FTP server. nxc ftp &lt;ip&gt; -u &lt;username&gt; -p &lt;password&gt; --get &lt;filename&gt; Expected Results: nxc ftp &lt;TARGET&g", "tags": []}